Wildfire is the special effect system for animations, image sequences and
images.
There are lots of new features - some of them are unique - but the
important thing to mention here is that Wildfire7\PPC is totally easy
to understand to anyone and user-friendly !

But it's not just an old program with a new GUI - we have
completely rewritten almost any part of it.

